'''莫天虎'''{{bd||}}，[[中國國民黨籍|中國國民黨籍]]政治人物，曾任[[中華民國|中華民國]]情治人員、[[內政部移民署|內政部移民署長]]、[[中國國民黨秘書長|中國國民黨秘書長]]。

== 生平 ==
莫天虎長年在[[法務部調查局|法務部調查局]]國家安全領域效力，行事謹慎擅於協調，擔任台北市調處主任時期，曾破過[[台北榮民總醫院|台北榮民總醫院]]密帳案<ref>{{cite news | author = 江元慶 | url = http://archive.businessweekly.com.tw/Article/Index?StrId=18637 | title = 榮總兩本密帳 被Ａ走二億六千萬 | publisher = [[商業周刊|商業周刊]] | date = 2004-07-08 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2017-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170823165412/http://archive.businessweekly.com.tw/Article/Index?StrId=18637 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，使得各家公立醫院開始清查小金庫，影響相當深遠；任職於台南調查站時，也曾破獲全國首宗[[非法|非法]][[竊聽|竊聽]]集團<ref>{{cite news | author = 張海燕 | url = http://tw.people.com.cn/BIG5/14812/14874/4475206.html | title = 台首破非法監聽集團 侵犯隱私且涉及暴力犯罪 | publisher = [[人民日報|人民日報]] | date = 2006-06-15 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2017-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170823165828/http://tw.people.com.cn/BIG5/14812/14874/4475206.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，雖然莫天虎掌管的是情報分析，但由於判讀精準，因此深受[[中華民國國家安全局|中華民國國家安全局]]、[[國家安全會議_(中華民國)|國安會]]青睞<ref>{{cite news|author=陶曉嫚、侯柏青|url=http://www.new7.com.tw/SNewsView.aspx?Key=%EF%BF%BD%25&i=TXT20160511173725O7E&p=9|title=莫天虎接任國民黨秘書長|publisher=[[新新聞|新新聞]]|date=2016-05-19|language=zh-TW|access-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823202830/http://www.new7.com.tw/SNewsView.aspx?Key=%EF%BF%BD%25&i=TXT20160511173725O7E&p=9|archive-date=2017-08-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

2014年5月20日，就任[[內政部移民署|內政部移民署長]]<ref>{{cite news|author=謝佳珍|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201405050266-1.aspx|title=內政部：莫天虎接移民署長|publisher=[[中央社|中央社]]|date=2014-05-05|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-23|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823164910/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201405050266-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=林慶川|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/776562|title=連升三級 莫天虎掌移民署|publisher=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|date=2014-05-06|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-23|archive-date=2019-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191201152841/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/focus/paper/776562|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = 劉宗龍 | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140520002634-260407 | title = 移民署署長 莫天虎走馬上任 | publisher = [[中時電子報|中時電子報]] | date = 2014-05-20 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191130011343/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20140520002634-260407 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年3月27日，時任[[中國國民黨主席|中國國民黨主席]][[洪秀柱|洪秀柱]]親自登門拜訪，力邀他出任[[中國國民黨秘書長|中國國民黨秘書長]]，起初雖未答應，但後來逐漸被洪的真誠感動，願意「雪中送炭」出任艱鉅，自願薪水砍半<ref>{{cite news|author=鄭媁|url=http://udn.com/news/story/1/1682610|title=掌黨秘書長 莫天虎：洪當選第二天就找我|publisher=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|date=2016-05-09|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2016-07-11|archive-date=2019-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503040429/https://udn.com/news/story/1/1682610|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1690498 | title = 情治秘書長莫天虎 洪秀柱「七顧茅廬」也要請來 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2016-05-09 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-11-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191130164208/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1690498 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=145110 | title = 被洪秀柱感動！國民黨秘書長莫天虎：只有她找過我 | publisher = [[三立新聞網|三立新聞網]] | date = 2016-05-09 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2016-05-28 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160528143024/http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=145110 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2016年5月9日，就任[[中國國民黨秘書長|中國國民黨秘書長]]<ref>{{cite news | url = https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/652266 | title = 國民黨新任秘書長莫天虎　調查局出身 | publisher = [[TVBS新聞網|TVBS新聞網]] | date = 2016-05-04 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190819214151/https://news.tvbs.com.tw/politics/652266 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://udn.com/news/story/1/1687573 | title = 接下國民黨秘書長職位 莫天虎上任 | publisher = [[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]] | date = 2016-05-04 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2016-07-11 | archive-date = 2021-06-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210602115357/https://udn.com/news/story/1/1687573 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = 施曉光 | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1684843 | title = 國民黨秘書長將由現任移民署長莫天虎擔任 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2016-05-04 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202075412/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/1684843 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = 郭匡超 | url = http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160504002639-260401 | title = 國民黨秘書長 傳移民署長莫天虎接任 | publisher = [[中時電子報|中時電子報]] | date = 2016-05-04 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202102356/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160504002639-260401 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，黨內人士認為，莫天虎符合[[洪秀柱|洪秀柱]]拋出四項條件，包括耐操耐磨、具調和鼎鼐能力、嫻熟行政立法運作、有相當黨政資歷，是相當適合的人選<ref>{{cite news | url = http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160504/852710/ | title = 調查局出身的移民署長莫天虎　將任國民黨秘書長 | publisher = [[蘋果日報_(台灣)|蘋果日報]] | author = 張文馨 | date = 2016-05-04 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2016-05-06 | archive-date = 2017-08-23 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170823165139/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20160504/852710/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=陳彥驊|url=https://www.nownews.com/news/20160504/2086795|title=莫天虎任國民黨祕書長　藍委：攜手發揮在野戰力|publisher=[[NOWnews|NOWnews]]|date=2016-05-04|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-23|archive-date=2019-11-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191129160341/https://www.nownews.com/news/20160504/2086795/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|author=周志豪|url=https://video.udn.com/news/486718|title=給需要的人幫助 莫天虎就任藍黨秘書長|publisher=[[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]]|date=2016-05-09|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-23|archive-date=2019-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190820165153/https://video.udn.com/news/486718|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年6月30日，[[中國國民黨主席|中國國民黨主席]][[洪秀柱|洪秀柱]]宣布提前卸任，與洪同進退退卸任秘書長一職<ref>{{cite news | author = 王寓中 | url = https://udn.com/news/story/10720/2496114 | title = 一級主管提前請辭？ 莫天虎：與柱同進退 | publisher = [[聯合新聞網|聯合新聞網]] | date = 2017-06-01 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-07-17 | archive-date = 2019-08-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190819032925/https://udn.com/news/story/10720/2496114 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | author = 施曉光 | url = http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2099893 | title = 洪秀柱宣布請辭 洪團隊全跟進退出黨中央 | publisher = [[自由時報|自由時報]] | date = 2017-06-14 | language = zh-TW | accessdate = 2017-08-23 | archive-date = 2019-12-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191202134848/https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2099893 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

== 軼聞 ==
莫天虎從過去任職調查局一直到移民署長，上下班都始終搭[[公共汽車|公車]]，從不在下班時間使用公務車輛，是少見的「公車署長」；每周回台中陪老母親，是自行搭乘[[國光客運|國光客運]]，不少媒體記者肯定他待人溝通誠懇，完全沒有官架子<ref name="謝明俊">{{cite news|author=謝明俊|url=http://m.cna.com.tw/magazine/51/201605160002.aspx|title=國民黨新任祕書長莫天虎 國光號的好朋友|publisher=時報周刊|date=2016-05-16|language=zh-TW|access-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823163046/http://m.cna.com.tw/magazine/51/201605160002.aspx|archive-date=2017-08-23|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

莫天虎本身熱愛運動，因緣際會下開始挑戰半馬，從原本忐忑不安到幾乎每年報名半馬，跑馬拉松跑出興趣；60歲首次挑戰全馬且完賽，並以5小時34分達陣<ref>{{cite news|author=謝佳珍|url=http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201703310095-1.aspx|title=從忐忑到興趣 莫天虎60歲挑戰全馬|publisher=[[中央社|中央社]]|date=2017-03-31|language=zh-TW|accessdate=2017-08-23|archive-date=2017-08-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823164152/http://www.cna.com.tw/news/aipl/201703310095-1.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

